reviewText: Some of the movies on here are just plain corny and not something an adult would enjoy; but an 8 year old might or a 10 year old or even a 12 year old. None of them are classics or superb movies. But there is a large enough selection that you should be able to find something most everyone can agree on. I particularly like that you get ten movies on two dvds in one package. It sure cuts down on space and waste of packaging like this. Bailey's Billions is a favorite for my children.Worth they Money.Enjoy.
